  <body>
    <section id="navigation">
      <div class="container-fluid">
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark">
          <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">furryfriends</a>
          <button
            class="navbar-toggler"
            type="button"
            data-bs-toggle="collapse"
            data-bs-target="#navbarCollapse"
            aria-controls="navbarCollapse"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-label="Toggle navigation"
          >
            <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
          </button>
          <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarCollapse">
            <ul class="navbar-nav me-auto mb-2 mb-md-0">
              <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link" aria-current="page" href="/">Home</a>
              </li>
              <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link active" href="/about">About</a>
              </li>
              <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link" href="/contact">Contact</a>
              </li>
              <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link" href="/dogs">Buy Dogs</a>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <form class="d-flex" action="/search" method="post">
              <input
                class="form-control me-2"
                type="search"
                name="search"
                placeholder="Search Dogs"
                aria-label="Search"
              />
              <button class="btn btn-outline-light" type="submit">
                Search
              </button>
            </form>
            <% if (isLoggedIn) { %>
            <div class="dropdown">
              <a
                class="nav-link dropdown-toggle"
                href="#"
                role="button"
                id="userDropdown"
                data-bs-toggle="dropdown"
                aria-expanded="false"
              >
                <img
                  src="<%= userPhotoUrl %>"
                  alt="Profile Photo"
                  class="rounded-circle mx-2"
                  width="30"
                  height="30"
                />
              </a>
              <ul class="dropdown-menu" aria-labelledby="userDropdown">
                <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/logout">Logout</a></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <% } %>
          </div>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about">
      <div class="container-fluid">
        <h1 class="heading">Our Vision</h1>
        <hr class="heading-underline" />
        <div
          class="row flex-lg-row-reverse align-items-center justify-content-center g-5 py-5"
        >
          <div class="col-10 col-sm-8 col-lg-4 d-flex justify-content-center">
            <img
              src="/assets/images/dog-img.jpg"
              class="d-block img-fluid about-img"
              alt="About Image"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <h1 class="mb-3 sub-heading">
              Our mission is to ensure that every dog finds a loving home and
              every owner experiences the joy of unconditional love and
              companionship.
            </h1>
            <hr class="sub-heading-underline" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
          <p class="question">
            What sets FurryFriends apart from other platforms offering puppies
            for sale?
          </p>
          <p class="answer">
            FurryFriends distinguishes itself by prioritizing the ethical
            treatment of animals and maintaining the highest standards of care
            for our puppies. Unlike many other platforms, we refuse to
            compromise on the well-being of our dogs. We work exclusively with
            breeders who uphold the highest ethical standards and ensure that
            every puppy is raised in a loving and healthy environment.
          </p>
          <p class="question">
            How does FurryFriends ensure the health and well-being of its
            puppies?
          </p>
          <p class="answer">
            At FurryFriends, we go above and beyond to ensure the health and
            well-being of our puppies. Before joining their new families, every
            puppy undergoes a comprehensive veterinary examination, receives
            necessary vaccinations, and undergoes deworming. We also conduct
            thorough screenings of our breeders' facilities and practices to
            ensure that they meet our strict standards for quality and care.
          </p>
          <p class="question">
            Can I trust that the puppies from FurryFriends are healthy and
            well-adjusted?
          </p>
          <p class="answer">
            Absolutely. We take the health and well-being of our puppies very
            seriously. Each puppy is carefully screened by a qualified
            veterinarian and receives a clean bill of health before being
            offered for sale. Additionally, we personally visit the breeders'
            facilities to ensure that the puppies are raised in a nurturing
            environment and are well-socialized.
          </p>
          <p class="question">
            How does FurryFriends support responsible pet ownership?
          </p>
          <p class="answer">
            FurryFriends is committed to promoting responsible pet ownership by
            providing our customers with the resources and support they need to
            care for their new furry companions. We offer guidance on puppy
            care, training, nutrition, and more to help ensure that every dog
            has a happy and healthy life with their new family.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

